# BaseCard API Query Tests
# READ-ONLY 테스트 - 데이터 조회만 테스트

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@aliceAddress = 0x1234567890123456789012345678901234567890
@bobAddress = 0x2345678901234567890123456789012345678901
@carolAddress = 0x3456789012345678901234567890123456789012

### ===========================================
### CARDS API - Query Tests
### ===========================================

### Get all cards
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cards

### Get Alice's card by address
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cards?address={{aliceAddress}}

### Get Bob's card by address
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cards?address={{bobAddress}}

### Get card by address (alternative endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/card/{{aliceAddress}}

### Get card by address (alternative endpoint - Bob)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/card/{{bobAddress}}

### ===========================================
### PROGRAMS API - Query Tests
### ===========================================

### Get all programs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/programs

### Get programs by type (bounty)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/programs?type=bounty

### Get programs by type (project)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/programs?type=project

### Get program by ID (assuming ID 1 exists)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/1

### Get program by ID (assuming ID 2 exists)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/program/2

### ===========================================
### COLLECTIONS API - Query Tests
### ===========================================

### Get collections for Alice's card (assuming card ID 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/collections?id=7

### Get collections for Bob's card (assuming card ID 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/collections?id=8

### Get collections for Carol's card (assuming card ID 3)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/collections?id=9

### Get all collections
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/collections

### ===========================================
### DEBUG API - Query Tests
### ===========================================

### Debug endpoint (if exists)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/debug
